title: Prime Minister welcomes vice-presidents of Libyan Presidential Council
text: Prime Minister, Mr Abdelaziz Djerad, welcomed, Wednesday at Algiers Houari Boumediene international airport, the two vice-presidents of the Libyan Presidential Council, Mr Moussa Al Koni and Mr Abdullah Al LAFI, on an official visit to Algeria on Wednesday and Thursday.
The Prime Minister was accompanied by Minister of Foreign Affairs, Mr Sabri Boukadoum, and Minister of the Interior, Local Authorities and National Planning, Mr Kamel Beldjoud.
